Working with Bchron Package

Trial for running Bchron I’ve already calibrated my radiocarbon dates with Calib, but I wanted to mess around with the Bchron package mostly to use the BchronDensity function to visualize my dates. I’m using this site: https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/Bchron/vignettes/Bchron.html for reference.
